Add the new [educationCategory](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/educationCategory?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

The scope **Members.Read.Hidden** is required to read or update the **Members** collection on an [educationClass](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/educationclass?view=graph-rest-1.0) entity using app-only tokens.
